Yawan mutanen da suka mutu a tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 832
Adadin mutanen da suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia ya kai 832, in ji hukumar kula da bala'i ta ƙasar a safiyar Lahadi.
An yi rahoton cewa an kama mutane da yawa a ƙarƙashin rufin da girgizar ƙasa ta 7.5 ta yi a ranar Juma'a kuma ta haifar da iska mai ƙarfi da ke da ƙafa 20, mai magana da yawun kamfanin Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya shaida wa taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, da ke da mutane fiye da 380,000, ya cika da ciyawa daga gidajen da suka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekara 32, a lokacin da ake bincike don kisan kai da aka yi wa wata mata
An soma bincike bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhard, Merseyside, da safiyar yau.
An gano mutumin mai shekara 44 a karfe 7:55 na safe a Grayson Mews da John Street, an kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 a binciken kisan kai.
'Yan sanda suna gayyatar duk wanda ya ga ko ya ji wani abu ya zo.
Sakataren 'Yan Sanda Brian O'Hagan ya ce: Binciken yana nan a farkonsa amma zan nemi duk wanda ya ga ko ya ji wani abu da ake zargi a filin jirgin sama na John Street a Birkenhead ya tuntube mu.
Ina so in tambayi kowa, musamman direbobin taksi, wanda zai iya samun wani abu a cikin dashkam don tuntuɓar mu saboda suna iya samun bayanai masu mahimmanci don bincikenmu.
