Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka yi a ranar Alhamis da aka ba da ta Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaɓa a Kotun Koli da kuma wata da aka zarge da yin fyade a shekara ta 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashar talabijin.
Yanzu da aka ci gaba da yin tawaye a siyasa, 'yan jarida sun daina yin shirye-shiryen da suka dace don a yi zaben na ƙarshe na ranar Juma'a: Majalisar Dokoki ta Arizona Jeff Flake ta yi yarjejeniya da FBI ta yi na mako guda don bincika zargin.
