Akwai yiwuwar cewa fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan bidiyon a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda Nielsen ta ruwaito.
Kamfanin yana karanta yawan kallon a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu lambobin nan take ba don sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Amma Nielsen yana fama da matsalar daidaita mutane a kamfanoninsa.
