Tashar Fox News, wadda masu shirya ta da hankali suka amince da zaben Kavanaugh, ta ratsa dukkan hanyoyin sadarwa ta hanyar samun matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin wannan ranar, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta ci gaba da kasancewa na biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.1, NBC tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.94, MSNBC tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
