HIV/Cutar zazzabin cizon sauro: Kasar Sin ta samu kashi 14% na sabon kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa tana da kasafin kashi 14% na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar sankarar cuta.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a birnin, in ji jami'an lafiya.
An yi sabon magana kusan 40,000 a cikin kashi na biyu na kwata na 2018 kawai.
Yawancin waɗannan sababbin kalmomin sun fito ne daga hanyar jima'i, suna nuna canji a dā.
A wasu sassan ƙasar Sin, cutar HIV ta yi sauri saboda an zubar da jini da ke dauke da cutar.
Amma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa sifili, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
A cikin shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar sankarar cuta ta ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i abu ne mai tsanani a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An soke batun jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma har yanzu ana kashe LGBT.
Domin dokokin tsaro na ƙasar, bincike ya annabta cewa maza da yawa da suka yi jima'i za su yi aure.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne ta wajen yin jima'i ba tare da yin jima'i ba.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV a matsayin wani mataki na yaki da cutar.
