Kamar yadda shugabannin Republican da yawa suka tsaya a gaban dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh a gaban zargin cin zarafin jima'i, masu bincike sun yi gargadin cewa za su ga sakamakon fushi da ya fito daga hannun mata, a lokacin zaben rabin gwamnati da ke zuwa.
Wannan ya jawo gagarumin sakamako, kuma an rubuta cewa yawancin 'yan Republican sun nuna sha'awar su ci gaba da yin zabe.
Ba za a iya dawo da bayanan ba, Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse ya shaida wa The Hill game da wani rubutu da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana ƙalubalanci matakin ƙarshe da Dan majalisar Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya ɗauka don cikakken binciken FBI don rage fushin masu jefa kuri'a.
Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru ba - ba za su manta da gobe ba sai a watan Nuwamba,  Karine Jean-Pierre, mai ba da shawara ga masu zane-zane da kuma mai magana da yawun wata kungiya mai suna MoveOn ta ce a ranar Juma'a, bisa ga jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun rera waka Nuwamba na zuwa! yayin da suke zanga-zangar a kan hanyar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya inda 'yan Republican suka zaɓi su ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh ta hanyar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya duk da ikirarin Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ya sanar.
Ƙarfin da kuma motsawar 'yan Democrat za su yi dabam, in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai bincike na siyasa da ba shi da haɗin kai da manema labarai.
 Mutane suna cewa ya tsufa; gaskiya ne.
