Kafin ma Ford ya yi sanarwa a fili game da zargin yin jima'i da aka yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, masu bincike sun yi hasashen cewa za a iya samun fushi idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da yin hakan.
Wannan ya zama babban rikici ga jam'iyyar GOP, in ji Michael Steele, shugaban jam'iyyar Republican One, a farkon babban mahaukaci, a cewar NBC News.
