Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi fushi ko kuma ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin da ya yi ikirarin, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
Bayan Flake ya yi magana, FBI ta yi bincike a kan zargin da Ford ya yi, kuma aƙalla wani mai zargin, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ta ruwaito.
