2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma tsunami ya yi tsananin tashin hankali a bakin tekun kudu, ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
