Alƙalai na gari suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin NYC
Alƙalai a birnin New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York da ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taɓa yi a jihar ba don aikata laifi a kowace ƙasa tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, an zarge shi da yin amfani da motar Home Depot don gyarawa kuma ya yi hatsarin a kan titin da ke kan titin West Highway a Lower Manhattan, kuma ya kashe masu tafiya da kuma masu tuƙi a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da dalilin da ya sa hukuncin kisa ya dace, alƙalai za su nuna cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi wa mutane da yawa lahani, a cikin wani tsari na neman hukuncin kisa, wanda Kotun Kudancin New York ta bayar.
Bisa ga takardar da kotun ta bayar, waɗannan tuhumar za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da tuhuma 22 da suka haɗa da zargin kisa takwas a lokacin hunturu, wanda alƙalai na tarayya ke amfani da su wajen yin magana da mutane, da kuma zargin yin faɗa da lalata mota.
Harin ya bukaci a yi shiri sosai, kuma a yi bincike sosai, in ji alƙalai, kuma a bayyana ayyukan da Saipov ya yi da suka sa ya zama mai lalata, mai lalata da kuma lalata.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo rauni, zalunci, da kuma hallaka ga dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar da aka yi.
Biyar daga cikin waɗanda aka kashe su matafiya ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe mutane biyu da sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na 2009.
A shekara ta 1953, an yi wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a kotun New York a karo na ƙarshe, ma'aurata da aka kashe a shekara ta 1953 don yin ƙulla yarjejeniya da za su yi wa Soviet Union ba'a a lokacin Yaƙin Cold.
A ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, an kashe Rosenberg biyu a kan kujera mai amfani da wutar lantarki.
Saipov, ɗan ƙasar Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin son kai a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, kamar yadda takardar kotu ta nuna.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa ya amince da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya gaya wa jami'an lasisi cewa abin da ya motsa shi ya kai harin shi ne kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, wanda zargin ya nuna.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a asibitinsa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ya yi laifi a kan zargin 22.
David Patton, wani mai ba da shawara ga jama'a a madadin Saipov, ya ce suna baƙin ciki sosai game da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar neman laifi na tsawon rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara tsoron abubuwan da ake yi ga duk wadanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Wani jami'in kare hakkin Saipov ya roƙi alƙalai su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisar Tory sun ce dole ne a sanya NIGEL FARAGE a kan shugaban kungiyar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin tattara sojojin jama'a a yau a lokacin zanga-zangar Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su samu 'yancin shiga' daga 'yan eurosceptics - inda wani dan majalisar dokokin kasar Theresa May ya kwatanta cewa ya kamata ya kasance a kan gaba a cikin kungiyar tarayyar Turai.
Shugaban jam'iyyar Conservative Peter Bone ya gaya wa jama'a a Birmingham a Birtaniya cewa za su tashi idan Mr Farage ya zama mai gabatar da kara na Brexit.
Amma Mrs May ta yi tunanin cewa sake haɗuwa da 'yan majalisa masu rabuwa ba daidai ba ne yayin da masu goyon bayan Tory suka shiga wani zanga-zanga na musamman don hana Brexit a cikin ƙasar.
Shugaban ya yi matukar damuwa da kiyaye tsarin yarjejeniyar Chequers a tsakanin hare-haren da Brexiteers, Remainers da EU suka kai.
Masu haɗin gwiwar sun nace cewa zai ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da zargi - kuma ya tilasta Eurosceptics da Labour su zaɓi daga cikin kunshin da ya yi da kuma 'Yarjejeniyar'.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa wani taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son a yi watsi da Chequers.
Ya kwatanta cewa dole ne a saka Mista Farage a cikin ƙungiyar kuma a ba shi aiki a kan tashar jiragen ruwa a tsakiyar Brussels.
"Idan ya kasance shugabanmu, ya kamata mu tafi yanzu", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: Zan tsaya a kan Brexit amma ya kamata mu yi watsi da Chequers.
A lokacin da yake nuna rashin amincewarsa da EU, ya ce: Ba mu yi yaƙi na duniya don mu yi biyayya ba.
Muna son mu yi dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.
Mista Boone ya rasa shawarwarin da ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun zaben 2016: Al'ummar Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son zama marasa gaskiya.
Tory mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ma yana wajen taron, yana gaya wa manema labarai: Na ce kawai: Firayim Minista, ku saurari mutane.
Mutane da yawa ba sa son Chequers, Masu sukar ba sa son su, jam'iyyunmu na siyasa da masu zanga-zangarmu ba sa son su, waɗanda suke yawo a tituna suna ganin an zabe mu.
Don Allah ka bar Chequers ka fara sauraro.
A cikin sakon da aka yi wa Mrs May, ta ce: Shugabannin gwamnati suna yin aiki ne a lokacin da suka cika alkawarinsu.
Mista Farage ya gaya wa taron cewa 'yan siyasa su samu 'yancin yin hakan idan suna son su tsere wa zaben 2016.
"Wannan yanzu magana ce ta amincewa tsakaninmu - mutane - da kuma 'yan siyasa", in ji shi.
Suna kokarin tserewa daga Brexit amma muna nan a yau don gaya musu ba za mu bar ku ba idan kun yi hakan
Saƙon da aka yi wa taron ya ce: Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasa da ke neman su tsere daga Brexit su ga yanayin zafi.
Mun haɗu da sojojin kasar nan da suka ba mu nasara a Brexit, ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai 'yanci, mai mulkin kai, mai daraja.
A wani ɓangare kuma, 'yan Remainers sun tashi daga Birmingham kafin taron kuma sun yi tafiya na sa'o'i biyu a birnin.
An fara taron 'yan adawa da ke kiran tutar Tory da Brexit a wannan makon.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Labour, Lord Adonis, ya gaya wa 'yan majalisa game da matsalar tsaro da suka fuskanta ta hanyar amfani da wata ƙungiya ta siyasa don buɗe taron.
Akwai mutanen da suka gaya mana cewa suna da tsarin IT da aka shirya tare da dukkan fasahar Kanada da ƙari da ƙari, don ƙasa da ƙasa, don kasuwanci kyauta da ƙasa a Ireland, ya kara da cewa.
Wannan ƙiyayya ce mai tsanani.
Babu wani abu kamar Brexit na gaske, ya kara da cewa.
Warren ya yi goyon baya sosai ga takarar shugaban kasa
