Saukar da Washington yana nufin amincewa da bukatun, amma yin magana da Amurka a gaban jama'a zai zama babban abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Masana sun yi ikirarin cewa idan Beijing ta yi nasara, za a iya samun ci gaba a harkokin kasuwanci na Amurka ta hanyar rage cinikayyar tattalin arzikin biyu.
Abubuwan da suka faru a cikin siyasa da suka faru a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayi da kuma fara rikice-rikice na tattalin arziki a cikin biranen biyu da suka fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu bincike suka yarda da su a baya, Abigail Grace, mai bincike da ke mayar da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Sabon Tsaro ta Amurka, ta ce.
Syria ta ba da tallafi ga 'yan gudun hijira su koma gida, Ministan Harkokin Wajen ya ce
Syria ta ce tana goyon bayan dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da kanta, tana neman taimako da kuma sake gina birnin da ya lalace bayan shekaru bakwai na yaƙi.
Da yake jawabi a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce halin da ake ciki a kasar yana ci gaba.
Ya ce a yau yanayin ƙasa yana da kyau kuma yana da aminci, godiya ga ci gaba da aka yi da kuma hana masu yin amfani da ita daga shiga,.
Gwamnati ta ci gaba da gyara yankunan da suka lalace don ta sake gina su.
Yanayin da ake ciki yanzu na dawo da 'yan gudun hijira daga ƙasashensu saboda rashin kula da gidaje da kuma tsarin tattalin arziki na al'umma da aka tsara don rayuwa da kuma sana'a.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce an rasa fiye da mutane miliyan 5.5 a Syria tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a 2011.
Har ila, mutane miliyan shida suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta amince da taimakon da za a ba ta kuma sake gina birnin.
Amma ya kuma nuna cewa ba zai amince da taimakon da ake bukata ko kuma daga al'ummomin da ke goyon bayan wannan rikici ba.
Turai ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar 2018 Ryder Cup ta hanyar cin nasarar Team USA da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16:5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a cikin tafiya zuwa Paris, Faransa.
A karo na uku ne Amurka ta yi nasara a gasar Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta dawo da kambin domin wani ɗan Denmark mai suna Thomas Bjorn ya ci nasara a kan Amirka da maki 14.5.
Shahararren dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala sosai a gasar, ya jefa kwallonsa cikin ruwa da bugun 3-a don ramin 16, ya rasa gasar a hannun Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi nasara sosai a lokacin, ya kasance mai wasan 1-in-4 don ya tafi 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amirka ya ci 5 da 4 a hannun Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark, wanda ya fi kowa yin wasan a Turai.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowacce nasara a duniya, ya ci nasara 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda ya yi nasara a gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
